"He would <EVENT eid="e61" class="I_STATE">like</EVENT> to <EVENT eid="e62" class="OCCURRENCE">straighten</EVENT> things out with (Jonathan) when the time comes," he <EVENT eid="e63" class="OCCURRENCE">said</EVENT>.

